    "tauschii resistance gene analogues (RGA1a-d, RGA2a-b, RGA3a) reported by Periyannan et al.",
    "24 (GenBank ID KF031285.1-KF031299.1).",
    "To confirm that this region is orthologous to the Mla locus in barley, we searched for the presence of the pumilio (Bpm) gene homologue and subtilisin-chymotrypsin inhibitor (CI) genes in gene-lifting annotations for AUS 18911, AUS 18913, CPI 110799 and TA1662.",
    "Bpm and CI genes were previously reported flanking Resistance Gene Homologues (RGH) of the Mla locus 83.",
    "The gene-lifting annotations were generated using liftoff v1.6.1 74 with default parameters based on the TA1675 genome annotation."
